<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Monday,
November, 8. If you have any questions, please call Ardua Harris on
the Star's News Desk at (816) 234-4753.
</P>
<P>
   ENGINEERED-CROPS-2TAKES LUBBOCK, Texas _ At the center of
gleaming government laboratories in Lubbock, tucked into petri
dishes nurturing man-made sprouts, coursing through roots of
genetically engineered seedlings, lives an idea.
</P>
<P>
