u i BC-R-PORTUGAL-REVIEW-ART     11-08 1239
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-PORTUGAL-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WISPS OF AN EMPIRE THAT TIME FORGOT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(ART ADV: Locator map is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(jt) 
