<P>
   Editors: The following items from The N.Y. Times Week in Review
for Sunday, Nov. 7, have moved:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ELIMINATE THE FOLLOWING SCHEDULED STORIES:
</P>
<P>
   EMOTION-CONTROL-REVIEW; COLOMBIA-VIOLENCE-REVIEW.  &LR;
</P>
