 &HT;    Create your dream toy
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Put on your creative caps because Amazon.com is
challenging you to design your dream toy. If the judges choose your
toy, it will be manufactured and sold on Amazon's Web site. You
have until Nov. 15 to mail in a 200-word description and a drawing
of your invention. There are two age categories: 8 and younger and
9 to 12. Twenty finalists from each category will be selected to
build a model of their toy and compete for the grand prize. Check
www.amazon.com for contest details.
</P>
