feet tall and the remote-control car is 10 feet long. And everybody
is on ice! ``Toy Story on Ice'' will be performed at Philips Arena
from Wednesday through Sunday. Tickets start at $12 for this
ice-skating adventure. Call 404-249-6400 for ticket information.
