<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-08 12:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2593 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-SPCL-AUTOS-MODELS-BOS     11-08 1596
