<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-08 14:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2724 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-UN-DEBT-BOS &LR;      11-08 1298
