in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-11-08-99 1449EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19991108.0242 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
