</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WHY-`GUY'-FLICKS-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE MASCULINITY CRISIS OF THE AMERICAN MALE  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 1,100-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 6 Nov. 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
