<P>
   FBN-COWBOYS-VIKINGS (Minneapolis) _ Dallas at Minnesota, 9 P.M.
The Vikings have won two straight with Jeff George taking the
snaps. For the Cowboys, Troy Aikman plans to play despite the
headaches caused by a helmet-to-helmet hit in last week's game
against the Colts. By Mike Freeman.
</P>
<P>
   BBO-MANAGERS (Dana Point, Calif.) _ The second day of the annual
