<P>
   BOXING
</P>
<P>
   BOX-LENNOX _ How has the life of Lennox Lewis changed since his
heavyweight fight with Evander Holyfield last March? In some ways,
it hasn't changed at all - he hasn't earned much respect in the
United States while he's still viewed as champion in Great Britian,
his home country. In other ways, his life has changed tremendously
- he's become the sentimental favorite in the boxing community
after the controversial draw nearly eight months ago. A profile of
Lewis heading into Saturday's heavyweight rematch against
Holyfield. (Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
