<P>
   MEXICO-ELECT _ MEXICO CITY _ With a landslide victory being
claimed by former interior minister Francisco Labastida Ochoa in
the first-ever nationwide PRI presidential primary, Mexico' s
ruling party is acting like it's already headed for victory in the
2000 presidential race. We update with more solid figures on
balloting and the possibility of a rupture. Developing. (Ferriss,
Cox News Service). 20.
