   HMOS-REAX _ HMOs in California were defensive Monday after
UnitedHealth Group said doctors, not its employees, will have the
final say on which treatments the nation's second-largest health
insurer will cover. By Jason Z. Cohen. (Will move on ``n''
California and ``f'' financial news wires.)
