</P>
<P>
   For information on bone marrow donation, contact the National
Marrow Donor Program at 1-800-627-7692 or visit the Internet site
at www.marrow.org.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  National Osteopathic Medicine Week
</P>
<P>
   Contact the American Osteopathic Association at 1-800-621-1773
or www.aoa-net.org.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  National Lung Cancer Awareness Day is Friday
</P>
<P>
   Contact the American Cancer Society at 1-800-227-2345 or at
www.cancer.org. Or, call the National Institutes of Health's Cancer
Information Service at 1-800-422-6237.
</P>
<P>
   _M.A.J. McKenna writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
