are preparing for worst-case WTO scenarios, including an act or
acts of bioterrorism. They are specifically preparing for the use
of smallpox, anthrax and botulism biohazards, as well as for
chemical spills and the like.
</P>
<P>
   By Carol Smith. (Story will move in the ``a'' category.)
