   HEALTHCARE-INSURE (Undated) _ United Health Group says it is
giving decision-making power over patient care back to physicians,
breaking with a longstanding element of managed care that has
infuriated many doctors and frustrated their patients. By Milt
Freudenheim. (We plan to move the story by 9:30 p.m. ET in ``f''
