<HEADLINE>
ROTISSERIE TO REALITY: INTERACTIVITY THE FUTURE OF INTERNET SPORTS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TOMMY CUMMINGS 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
 
